data.description: Welcome to Webster! Bring you creativity to make this your dream home. This home features 3-bedrooms, 2-bathroooms and a 2 car garage. Fenced yard... fenced to the slope. Bonus room in back yard can be used as retreat, exercise room, game room, or...Quiet cul-du-sac, top of the street with potential views to the rear. The property will require some repairs. Come and check out this gem in the rough.
